import { SET_DASHBOARD } from "../actions/types";

const initialState = {
    loading: false,
    success: false,
    error: false,
    data: {},
    message: '',
}

export default function(state = initialState, action) {
    switch (action.type) {
      case SET_DASHBOARD:
        return {
          ...state,
          success: true,
          data: action.payload
        };
      default:
        return state;
    }
  }
